title: Episode 180: The one that got away (Feat. Vado)

description:
Rapper Vado joins the ladies of Lip Service and breaks the time he was cat-fished, why he doesn't like his nipples played with, why your girl shouldn't be close with your mom, and much more! Angela and Vado open up about their previous relationship and things get awkward when Lore'l asks the difficult question...Enjoy! ***LIVE SHOW ALERT*** When: Thursday, March 28, 2019 at 7:30pm Location: Caroline's on Broadway - NYC TIckets: https://www.ticketweb.com/event/lip-service-live-carolines-on-broadway-tickets/
